                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                            What is a decision matrix?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            A decision matrix is a systematic tool that helps you evaluate and prioritize different options based on specific criteria. It works by:
                            <ul>
                                <li>Listing all your available options</li>
                                <li>Defining important criteria for evaluation</li>
                                <li>Weighting these criteria based on importance</li>
                                <li>Scoring each option against the criteria</li>
                                <li>Calculating a final score to determine the best choice</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

