                            <ul>
                                <li>10 = Extremely important</li>
                                <li>7-9 = Very important</li>
                                <li>4-6 = Moderately important</li>
                                <li>1-3 = Slightly important</li>
                            </ul>
                            Consider how important each criterion is relative to others. Not everything can be a 10!
                        </div>
